wolf-shaper: Wolf Shaper is a free and open source distortion/waveshaper plugin.
wolf-shaper: Rather than tweaking abstract knobs, you draw the shaping curve
wolf-shaper: directly on an interactive spline-based graph, giving instant
wolf-shaper: visual feedback on how the waveform will be transformed.
wolf-shaper:
wolf-shaper: Built with the DISTRHO Plugin Framework (DPF), this package
wolf-shaper: provides CLAP, DSSI, LV2, VST2 and VST3 plugin formats plus a
wolf-shaper: standalone JACK application.
